# since Cost Center Allocation/Packing Slip/Supplier Scorecard Period's own leaf shape — NINE
# Link -> Quality Inspection fields (seven non-submittable child-table rows + the
# self-referencing amended_from + Job Card, the one genuine submittable edge). CAVEAT: FIVE
# whitelisted methods (another dossier correction — its own §9 claimed four, treating
# make_quality_inspection as undecorated; verified @frappe.whitelist() at quality_inspection.py:
# 487) — nothing granted toward any of them.
# Installation Note added 2026-07-21 (breadth campaign Wave 4, fifth row) — the twenty-seventh
# governed doctype, same run_method submit/cancel surface; Wave 4's SECOND ROW WITH A REAL PARTY
# FIELD (party_field="customer", a required header-level Link — Quality Inspection/Cost Center
